WEBVTT

00:00:01.857 --> 00:00:03.460
- COLE: Good night, princess.

00:00:04.508 --> 00:00:06.188
- JODIE: Is Nathan okay?

00:00:06.731 --> 00:00:08.464
When will I see him again?

00:00:09.461 --> 00:00:10.661
- COLE: (SIGHS)

00:00:11.493 --> 00:00:13.093
I don't know, honey.

00:00:13.677 --> 00:00:16.502
He hasn't left his office since three days.

00:00:18.378 --> 00:00:22.346
He loved his wife and daughter
more than anything in the world.

00:00:25.026 --> 00:00:27.426
But we can try again tomorrow, okay?

00:00:34.534 --> 00:00:36.054
You get some sleep.

00:00:42.856 --> 00:00:43.856
(DOOR SHUTS)

00:00:53.943 --> 00:00:56.276
(OMINOUS NOISE)

00:02:14.291 --> 00:02:16.386
- NATHAN: (CRYING)

00:02:22.845 --> 00:02:23.845
Jodie.

00:02:25.913 --> 00:02:28.179
What're you doing here? It's late.

00:02:29.010 --> 00:02:30.210
Go back to bed.

00:02:53.163 --> 00:02:55.625
- JODIE: (IN LAURA VOICE)
Don't be sad, daddy.

00:02:55.651 --> 00:02:57.331
- NATHAN: (QUIETLY)
What?

00:02:57.762 --> 00:02:59.122
What did you say?

00:02:58.985 --> 00:03:00.460
- JODIE: (IN LAURA VOICE)
It was so quick.

00:03:01.592 --> 00:03:03.893
Mommy couldn't do anything.

00:03:05.898 --> 00:03:07.589
But it didn't hurt.

00:03:07.732 --> 00:03:08.827
- NATHAN: Stop it, Jodie!

00:03:08.573 --> 00:03:10.519
- JODIE: (IN LAURA VOICE)
It didn't hurt at all.

00:03:10.186 --> 00:03:12.512
- NATHAN: You hear me?
Stop it right now!

00:03:12.322 --> 00:03:15.189
- JODIE: (IN HELEN VOICE)
We are here, Nathan.

00:03:17.141 --> 00:03:18.821
We're right by your side.

00:03:20.039 --> 00:03:21.319
- NATHAN: Helen.

00:03:22.040 --> 00:03:23.040
Laura.

00:03:22.965 --> 00:03:25.909
- JODIE: (IN HELEN VOICE)
We love you, darling.

00:03:26.117 --> 00:03:28.180
We'll always love you.

00:03:29.223 --> 00:03:31.023
- NATHAN: Talk to me again.

00:03:30.827 --> 00:03:31.827
Jodie!

00:03:32.522 --> 00:03:35.466
Make them come back.
Make them come back again!

00:03:35.938 --> 00:03:38.004
- JODIE: I can't. They've gone.

00:03:39.860 --> 00:03:41.220
- NATHAN: Please.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:43.040
Don't leave me.

00:03:43.676 --> 00:03:45.199
Don't leave me.

00:03:49.244 --> 00:03:51.451
I miss them so much.